  "docsFreelancerWelcomeContent": "En tant que pigiste sur Aura In, vous offrez des services directement aux clients de votre région. Contrairement à un magasin traditionnel, vous travaillez de votre propre emplacement et pouvez vous déplacer pour rencontrer les clients. Configurez votre profil en quelques minutes et commencez à accepter des réservations.",
  "docsFreelancerVsShopTitle": "Pigiste vs Magasin: Quelle est la différence?",
  "docsFreelancerVsShopContent": "Voici comment fonctionne le travail indépendant:",
  "docsFreelancerIndependent": "Vous travaillez de façon indépendante - aucun magasin fixe requis",
  "docsFreelancerTravel": "Vous pouvez vous déplacer vers les clients dans votre rayon choisi",
  "docsFreelancerHours": "Vous définissez vos propres heures et disponibilité",
  "docsFreelancerManage": "Vous gérez votre propre horaire et vos clients",
  "docsFreelancerBooking": "Les clients vous réservent directement pour les services",
  "docsFreelancerRequirementsTitle": "Ce dont vous aurez besoin",
  "docsFreelancerRequirementsContent": "Pour commencer en tant que pigiste, vous avez besoin de: votre nom, un type de profession (coiffeur, thérapeute de massage, etc.), emplacement, rayon de voyage, services et vos heures de travail. Une photo professionnelle aide les clients à vous faire confiance.",
  "docsProfileSetupTitle": "Créez votre profil",
  "docsProfileSetupSubtitle": "Dites aux clients qui vous êtes",
  "docsProfilePhotoTitle": "Ajoutez votre photo de profil",
  "docsProfilePhotoContent": "Un portrait professionnel crée la confiance chez les clients. Utilisez une photo claire et bien éclairée de vous. Les clients veulent savoir avec qui ils réservent.",
  "docsYourNameTitle": "Votre nom",
  "docsYourNameContent": "Entrez votre nom complet exactement comme vous voulez que les clients le voient. Soyez professionnel et clair.",
  "docsProfessionTypeTitle": "Choisissez votre profession",
  "docsProfessionTypeContent": "Sélectionnez ce que vous faites. Exemples: Coiffeur, Thérapeute de massage, Maquilleur, Barbier, Esthéticienne ou autres services spécialisés.",
  "docsBioDescriptionTitle": "Écrivez votre bio",
  "docsBioDescriptionContent": "Écrivez une brève description sur vous et votre expérience (50-150 mots). Dites aux clients ce qui vous rend spécial. Exemple: \"Je me spécialise dans les soins naturels des cheveux avec 5 ans d'expérience. Certifié en coloration et coiffage.\"",
  "docsTermsGuidelinesTitle": "Ajoutez vos directives",
  "docsTermsGuidelinesContent": "Partagez les règles ou politiques importantes. Exemples: restrictions d'âge, politique d'annulation, exigences de santé ou instructions de préparation.",
  "docsServiceAreaTitle": "Définissez votre zone de service",
  "docsServiceAreaSubtitle": "Définissez où vous travaillez",
  "docsBaseLocationTitle": "Définissez votre emplacement de base",
  "docsBaseLocationContent": "C'est où vous travaillez normalement. Les clients dans votre rayon de voyage peuvent vous réserver. Vous pouvez soit épingler sur la carte, soit rechercher votre adresse.",
  "docsTravelRadiusTitle": "Rayon de voyage",
  "docsTravelRadiusContent": "Jusqu'où êtes-vous prêt à voyager pour rencontrer les clients? Définissez cela en kilomètres. Exemple: \"rayon de 5 km\" signifie que les clients jusqu'à 5 km de votre emplacement peuvent vous réserver.",
  "docsMobileVsFixedTitle": "Mobile ou emplacement fixe?",
  "docsMobileVsFixedContent": "Choisissez si vous vous déplacez vers les clients ou les rencontrez à un endroit. Si vous êtes mobile, les clients peuvent vous demander à leur domicile ou au bureau.",
  "docsServiceAddressTip": "Les clients verront votre rayon de voyage lors de la recherche. Soyez précis pour qu'ils sachent si vous pouvez servir leur région.",
  "docsToolsSetupTitle": "Énumérez vos outils et équipements",
  "docsToolsSetupSubtitle": "Montrez aux clients ce que vous apportez",
  "docsToolsIntroTitle": "Que sont les outils?",
  "docsToolsIntroContent": "Les outils sont l'équipement ou les compétences que vous possédez. Ils aident les clients à comprendre ce que vous pouvez faire et à quoi s'attendre.",
  "docsToolExamplesTitle": "Outils d'exemple",
  "docsToolExamplesContent": "Pour différentes professions:",
  "docsToolHairdresser": "Coiffeur: Sèche-cheveux, lisseur, fer à friser, ciseaux",
  "docsToolMassage": "Thérapeute de massage: Table de massage, pierres chaudes, huiles d'aromathérapie",
  "docsToolMakeup": "Maquilleur: Pinceaux à maquillage, aérographe, lumière LED",
  "docsToolBarber": "Barbier: Tondeuses électriques, rasoir droit, crème coiffante",
  "docsToolSelectionTitle": "Sélection d'outils",
  "docsToolSelectionContent": "Choisissez tous les outils et équipements que vous utilisez professionnellement. Les clients veulent savoir que vous disposez du bon équipement pour leur service.",
  "docsServicesSetupTitle": "Services et tarification",
  "docsServicesSetupSubtitle": "Dites aux clients ce que vous proposez",
  "docsServiceBasicsTitle": "Ajoutez vos services",
  "docsServiceBasicsContent": "Chaque service est quelque chose que les clients peuvent réserver. Exemples: \"Coupe de cheveux\", \"Massage complet du corps\", \"Application de maquillage\".",
  "docsServiceInfoTitle": "Pour chaque service, ajoutez:",
  "docsServiceInfoContent": "Tu as besoin:",
  "docsServiceInfoName": "Nom du service - ce que vous proposez",
  "docsServiceInfoDescription": "Description - ce qui est inclus",
  "docsServiceInfoPrice": "Prix - combien ça coûte",
  "docsServiceInfoDuration": "Durée - combien de temps cela prend (30 min, 1 heure, etc.)",
  "docsPricingStrategyTitle": "Conseils de tarification",
  "docsPricingStrategyContent": "Recherchez ce que les autres facturent pour des services similaires dans votre région. Tarifiez de façon compétitive mais équitable pour votre niveau d'expérience.",
  "docsDurationImportanceFreelancer": "Définissez la durée avec précision. C'est ainsi que vous bloquez le temps pour chaque réservation. Les clients dépendent de ce temps.",
  "docsHoursSetupTitle": "Définissez votre disponibilité",
  "docsHoursSetupSubtitle": "Quand êtes-vous disponible pour travailler",
  "docsHoursIntroTitle": "Heures de travail",
  "docsHoursIntroContent": "Les clients ne peuvent réserver que pendant les heures que vous marquez comme disponibles. Définissez vos heures pour chaque jour de la semaine.",
  "docsFlexibleHoursTitle": "Flexible ou strict?",
  "docsFlexibleHoursContent": "Vous décidez. Si vous voulez des heures régulières, définissez-les. Si vous préférez la flexibilité, vous pouvez ajuster quotidiennement selon vos besoins.",
  "docsBlockTimeTip": "Quand un client vous réserve, ce temps est bloqué dans votre calendrier. Définissez les heures judicieusement pour éviter les conflits.",
  "docsContactCredentialsTitle": "Informations de contact et références d'identification",
  "docsContactCredentialsSubtitle": "Aidez les clients à vous joindre et à générer de la confiance",
  "docsCreateProductTitle": "Vendre des produits en ligne",
  "docsCreateProductSubtitle": "Listez des articles à vendre et atteignez les clients de votre région",
  "docsProductOverviewTitle": "Premiers pas dans la vente de produits",
  "docsProductOverviewSubtitle": "Apprenez comment lister et vendre des articles",
  "docsProductWelcomeTitle": "Bienvenue à la vente de produits",
  "docsProductWelcomeContent": "Vendez des produits physiques directement aux clients de votre région. Des articles faits à la main aux biens de détail, vous pouvez atteindre les clients qui recherchent ce que vous offrez.",
  "docsPhoneRequirementTitle": "Vous avez besoin d'un numéro de téléphone vérifié",
  "docsPhoneRequirementContent": "Avant de pouvoir commencer à vendre des produits, vous devez vérifier votre numéro de téléphone. Ceci est pour la communication avec les clients et pour valider votre identité.",
  "docsAddPhoneNumberTitle": "Comment ajouter votre numéro de téléphone",
  "docsAddPhoneNumberContent": "Allez à les paramètres de votre profil et ajoutez votre numéro de téléphone. Vous recevrez un code de vérification par SMS pour confirmer que c'est vraiment votre numéro. Cela prend juste une minute.",
  "docsWhyPhoneVerifiedTitle": "Pourquoi la vérification du téléphone?",
  "docsWhyPhoneVerifiedContent": "Un numéro de téléphone vérifié crée la confiance des clients et nous permet de vous contacter s'il y a des problèmes. Cela aide également à prévenir la fraude.",
  "docsPhoneImportant": "Vous ne pouvez pas lister des produits jusqu'à ce que vous ayez un numéro de téléphone vérifié. Ceci est obligatoire pour tous les vendeurs.",
  "docsProductBasicsTitle": "Informations de base du produit",
  "docsProductBasicsSubtitle": "Ce que vous devez dire aux clients à propos de votre produit",
  "docsProductNameTitle": "Nom du produit",
  "docsProductNameContent": "Entrez le nom de votre produit clairement. Les clients recherchent par nom de produit, alors soyez précis. Exemple: \"Portefeuille en cuir fait à la main - Marron\" au lieu de simplement \"Portefeuille\".",
  "docsProductDescriptionTitle": "Description du produit",
  "docsProductDescriptionContent": "Écrivez une description détaillée. Dites aux clients ce que c'est, de quoi c'est fait, comment l'utiliser et pourquoi c'est bon. Soyez honnête sur l'état (nouveau, utilisé, remis à neuf).",
  "docsCategorySelectionTitle": "Choisissez une catégorie",
  "docsCategorySelectionContent": "Sélectionnez la bonne catégorie. Les clients parcourent par catégorie pour trouver des articles, donc la précision est importante. Choisissez la catégorie la plus spécifique disponible.",
  "docsProductConditionTitle": "État du produit",
  "docsProductConditionContent": "Soyez clair sur l'état: Neuf (jamais utilisé), Comme neuf (utilisé une fois), Bon (légère usure), Passable (usure visible) ou Tel quel. L'honnêteté crée la confiance.",
  "docsPricingStockTitle": "Prix et disponibilité",
  "docsPricingStockSubtitle": "Définissez votre prix et gérez les stocks",
  "docsPricingTitle": "Définissez votre prix",
  "docsPricingContent": "Définissez un prix équitable en fonction de l'état, de la valeur marchande et de la demande locale. Les clients peuvent voir des articles similaires, donc les prix compétitifs aident.",
  "docsCurrencyTitle": "Devise",
  "docsCurrencyContent": "Les prix sont affichés dans la devise de votre magasin. Assurez-vous que la devise de votre magasin est correctement définie avant d'ajouter des produits.",
  "docsStockQuantityTitle": "Quantité en stock",
  "docsStockQuantityContent": "Entrez le nombre d'articles que vous avez. Quand le stock s'épuise, le produit s'affiche comme indisponible. Mettez à jour ceci au fur et à mesure que vous vendez des articles.",
  "docsStockTip": "Gardez le stock exact. Les clients s'énervent s'ils commandent quelque chose qui est en rupture de stock. Mettez à jour régulièrement au fur et à mesure que vous vendez.",
  "docsProductPhotosTitle": "Photos de produit",
  "docsProductPhotosSubtitle": "Montrez aux clients ce qu'ils achètent",
  "docsPhotosImportanceTitle": "Les photos comptent le plus",
  "docsPhotosImportanceContent": "De bonnes photos sont essentielles. Les clients décident d'acheter en fonction des photos. Mauvaises photos = moins de ventes.",
  "docsWhatPhotosTitle": "Quoi photographier",
  "docsWhatPhotosContent": "Prenez des photos qui montrent le produit réel:",
  "docsPhotoFull": "Produit complet sous plusieurs angles",
  "docsPhotoCloseups": "Gros plans des détails et de la qualité",
  "docsPhotoCondition": "Photos montrant l'état (s'il est utilisé)",
  "docsPhotoScale": "Photos à côté de quelque chose pour l'échelle (comme une pièce ou une main)",
  "docsPhotoDamage": "Photos de dommages ou usure (l'honnêteté crée la confiance)",
  "docsPhotoTipsTitle": "Conseils de qualité photo",
  "docsPhotoTipsContent": "Utilisez la lumière naturelle. Prenez des photos sur fond propre. Montrez les couleurs avec précision. N'utilisez pas de filtres qui changent l'apparence du produit.",
  "docsPhotoCountTitle": "Combien de photos?",
  "docsPhotoCountContent": "Téléchargez au moins 3 photos claires. Plus de photos aident les clients à mieux comprendre le produit. Limitez à 10 photos par produit.",
  "docsToolsTitle": "Outils commerciaux",
  "docsToolsSubtitle": "Fonctionnalités puissantes pour automatiser, promouvoir et gérer votre entreprise",
  "docsToolsOverviewTitle": "Aperçu des outils",
  "docsToolsOverviewSubtitle": "Ce que chaque outil fait et comment l'utiliser",
  "docsToolsWelcomeTitle": "Bienvenue aux outils commerciaux",
  "docsToolsWelcomeContent": "L'onglet Outils dispose de 8 fonctionnalités puissantes pour vous aider à automatiser, promouvoir et gérer votre entreprise de manière plus efficace. Chaque outil résout un problème commercial spécifique.",
  "docsToolsListTitle": "Outils disponibles",
  "docsToolsListContent": "Vous avez accès à ces 8 outils:",
  "docsToolsReminders": "Rappels automatisés - Envoyer des rappels aux clients",
  "docsToolsPromotions": "Gestionnaire de promotions - Créer et gérer les remises",
  "docsToolsExport": "Rapports d'exportation - Téléchargez vos données commerciales",
  "docsToolsPayment": "Paramètres de paiement - Configurez comment vous recevez les paiements",
  "docsToolsHours": "Heures commerciales - Définissez votre horaire de travail",
  "docsToolsServices": "Gestion des services - Ajouter et modifier vos services",
  "docsToolsLoyalty": "Programme de fidélité - Récompensez les clients réguliers",
  "docsToolsBroadcasts": "Diffusions - Envoyez des messages à vos clients",
  "docsRemindersTitle": "1. Rappels automatisés",
  "docsRemindersSubtitle": "Envoyer des rappels automatiques aux clients",
  "docsReminderPurposeTitle": "Ce qu'il fait",
  "docsReminderPurposeContent": "Envoyer automatiquement des messages de rappel aux clients avant leurs réservations. Réduit les absences et maintient les clients informés.",
  "docsReminderBenefitsTitle": "Avantages",
  "docsReminderBenefitsContent": "Les rappels automatisés vous aident à:",
  "docsReminderBenefitNoShow": "Réduire les absences - les clients oublient moins probablement",
  "docsReminderBenefitExperience": "Améliorer l'expérience client - ils savent quand arriver",
  "docsReminderBenefitTime": "Économiser du temps - pas besoin d'appeler ou d'envoyer des messages manuellement",
  "docsReminderBenefitReliability": "Augmenter la fiabilité - les rappels sortent automatiquement",
  "docsReminderSetupTitle": "Comment le configurer",
  "docsReminderSetupContent": "Cliquez sur \"Configurer les rappels automatisés\" pour définir l'heure: envoyer des rappels 24 heures avant, 2 heures avant ou le matin de la nomination.",
  "docsReminderImpact": "Les magasins utilisant des rappels automatisés voient 20-30% moins d'absences. Cela affecte directement vos revenus.",
  "docsPromosTitle": "2. Gestionnaire de promotions",
  "docsPromosSubtitle": "Créer des offres spéciales et des remises",
  "docsPromosPurposeTitle": "Ce qu'il fait",
  "docsPromosPurposeContent": "Créez des promotions et des remises à temps limité. Offrir un pourcentage de réduction, un montant fixe de réduction ou des modules complémentaires gratuits pour attirer plus de clients.",
  "docsPromosExamplesTitle": "Idées de promotion",
  "docsPromosExamplesContent": "Vous pouvez créer des promotions comme:",
  "docsPromosExample1": "20% de réduction sur les coupes de cheveux le lundi",
  "docsPromosExample2": "Huile de massage gratuite avec toute réservation de massage",
  "docsPromosExample3": "50 de réduction sur un forfait de service complet",
  "docsPromosExample4": "Client pour la première fois: 30% de réduction",
  "docsPromosExample5": "Bonus de fidélité: 5e service à moitié prix",
  "docsPromosStrategyTitle": "Stratégie de promotion",
  "docsPromosStrategyContent": "Utilisez les promotions pendant les périodes creuses pour augmenter les réservations. Suivez quelles promotions fonctionnent le mieux grâce à votre analyse.",
  "docsExportTitle": "3. Rapports d'exportation",
  "docsExportSubtitle": "Téléchargez vos données pour analyse",
  "docsExportPurposeTitle": "Ce qu'il fait",
  "docsExportPurposeContent": "Téléchargez des rapports détaillés de vos données commerciales au format feuille de calcul. Analysez les réservations, les revenus, les clients, et plus.",
  "docsExportTypesTitle": "Rapports disponibles",
  "docsExportTypesContent": "Vous pouvez exporter:",
  "docsExportBookings": "Rapports de réservation - toutes les réservations avec détails",
  "docsExportRevenue": "Rapports de revenus - les bénéfices par plage de dates",
  "docsExportCustomers": "Rapports clients - votre liste de clients",
  "docsExportServices": "Rapports de services - performance par service",
  "docsExportWorkers": "Rapports de travailleurs - mesures de performance du personnel",
  "docsExportUsesTitle": "Pourquoi exporter les données?",
  "docsExportUsesContent": "Utilisez les données exportées dans Excel pour une analyse personnalisée, la tenue de registres, à des fins fiscales ou pour partager avec un comptable.",
  "docsTimeSlotsTitle": "Créneaux horaires expliqués",
  "docsTimeSlotsSubtitle": "Comprendre le fonctionnement des heures de réservation",
  "docsTimeSlotsOverviewTitle": "Que sont les créneaux horaires?",
  "docsTimeSlotsOverviewSubtitle": "Apprenez comment le système de programmation fonctionne",
  "docsTimeSlotsWelcomeTitle": "Bienvenue aux créneaux horaires",
  "docsTimeSlotsWelcomeContent": "Les créneaux horaires sont les heures disponibles où les clients peuvent réserver vos services. Comprendre leur fonctionnement vous aide à gérer votre horaire efficacement.",
  "docsTimeSlotsBasicsTitle": "Principes fondamentaux des créneaux horaires",
  "docsTimeSlotsBasicsContent": "Voici comment fonctionnent les créneaux horaires:",
  "docsTimeSlotsPoint1": "Chaque service a une durée (combien de temps il faut)",
  "docsTimeSlotsPoint2": "Vous définissez vos heures disponibles (quand vous travaillez)",
  "docsTimeSlotsPoint3": "Le système crée des créneaux horaires basés sur la durée du service",
  "docsTimeSlotsPoint4": "Les clients ne peuvent réserver que les créneaux disponibles",
  "docsTimeSlotsExampleTitle": "Exemple: Créer des créneaux horaires",
  "docsTimeSlotsExampleContent": "Si vous proposez une coupe de cheveux de 30 minutes et que vous travaillez de 9 h à 17 h:\n• 9h00 - 9h30 (Créneau 1)\n• 9h30 - 10h00 (Créneau 2)\n• 10h00 - 10h30 (Créneau 3)\n...et ainsi de suite toute la journée",
  "docsTimeSlotsOverlapTitle": "Et si les services se chevauchent?",
  "docsTimeSlotsOverlapContent": "Si vous avez plusieurs membres du personnel, chaque personne a son propre horaire. Si vous travaillez seul, un seul client peut réserver à la fois — le système bloque automatiquement les heures en conflit.",
  "docsTimeSlotsGapTitle": "Définir des écarts entre les services",
  "docsTimeSlotsGapContent": "Vous pouvez définir le temps tampon entre les réservations. Exemple: 15 minutes d'écart après chaque coupe de cheveux pour le nettoyage. Cela réduit les créneaux disponibles mais vous donne de la respiration.",
  "docsTimeSlotsGroupTitle": "Réservations de groupe et créneaux horaires",
  "docsTimeSlotsGroupContent": "Pour les réservations de groupe, le système trouve des heures qui conviennent à TOUTES les personnes du groupe. Cela rend plus difficile la recherche de créneaux disponibles, mais garantit que tout le monde est servi ensemble.",
  "docsTimeSlotsBlockingTitle": "Temps de blocage",
  "docsTimeSlotsBlockingContent": "Vous pouvez bloquer manuellement le temps pour le déjeuner, les pauses ou les rendez-vous personnels. Le temps bloqué n'apparaîtra pas comme disponible pour les clients.",
  "docsTimeSlotsUtilizationTitle": "Maximiser vos créneaux horaires",
  "docsTimeSlotsUtilizationContent": "Conseils pour utiliser vos créneaux efficacement:\n• Faites correspondre la durée du service à la réalité (ne sous-estimez pas)\n• Définissez des écarts réalistes entre les services\n• Utilisez le temps tampon de manière stratégique\n• Passez en revue et ajustez en fonction des commentaires des clients",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_title": "What is Aura In?",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_subtitle": "Understand the platform",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_welcomeIntroTitle": "Welcome to Aura In",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_welcomeIntroContent": "Aura In is a mobile marketplace connecting service professionals with customers. Whether you offer haircuts, massages, freelance services, or sell products, this platform helps you grow your business.",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_whoUsesAppTitle": "Who Uses Aura In?",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_whoUsesAppContent": "Two types of users power the platform:",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_whoUsesAppBullet1": "Service Providers - Salons, spas, barbers, freelancers who offer services",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_whoUsesAppBullet2": "Customers - People searching for and booking services in their area",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_whoUsesAppBullet3": "Product Sellers - Shops selling retail products or handmade items",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_howItWorksTitle": "How It Works",
  "docsGettingStartedWhatIsNanoembryo_howItWorksContent": "Service providers create a profile, list their services with pricing, and accept bookings from customers. Customers search by location, browse services, and book appointments. Everything is managed through the app.",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_title": "Three Ways to Use Aura In",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_subtitle": "Choose your role",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_optionCustomerTitle": "Option 1: Browse & Book Services (Customer)",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_optionCustomerContent": "Search for salons, massage therapists, barbers, or freelancers near you. View their services, pricing, and availability. Book appointments directly through the app and pay securely.",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_guestBookingTitle": "Guest Booking (No App Download Needed)",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_guestBookingContent": "Don't want to download the app? Service providers can share a booking link - you can book and pay directly through that link without creating an account. Your booking details and receipt will be sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_optionProviderTitle": "Option 2: Offer Services (Shop Owner or Freelancer)",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_optionProviderContent": "Create a shop or freelancer profile, list your services with pricing and duration, set your working hours, and manage bookings. Get paid for every service booked.",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_optionSellerTitle": "Option 3: Sell Products (Product Seller)",
  "docsGettingStartedThreeUserTypes_optionSellerContent": "If you make handmade items or sell products, you can list them for sale. Customers browse and purchase directly from your shop.",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_title": "Platform Features",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_subtitle": "What you can do",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewTitle": "Core Platform Features",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewContent": "Aura In includes everything you need to run a service business:",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet1": "Booking System - Customers book services, you manage calendar",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet2": "Secure Payments - Accept payments via Paystack or Stripe",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet3": "Real-time Chat - Communicate with customers before/after bookings",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet4": "Location-based Search - Customers find you by location using Google Maps",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet5": "Business Dashboard - Analytics, revenue tracking, client management",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet6": "Team Management - Add staff members and assign them to services",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet7": "Automated Reminders - Send appointment reminders to reduce no-shows",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet8": "Promotions & Loyalty - Run discounts and reward repeat customers",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet9": "Product Selling - List items for sale if you offer products",
  "docsGettingStartedKeyFeatures_featuresOverviewBullet10": "Reviews & Ratings - Build trust through customer feedback",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_title": "For Customers",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_subtitle": "How to find and book services",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerStartTitle": "Getting Started as a Customer",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerStartContent": "Create an account, set your location, and start searching for services. You can view service providers near you, read reviews, check pricing, and book appointments.",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesTitle": "Customer Capabilities",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesContent": "As a customer, you can:",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet1": "Search services by location (using Google Maps)",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet2": "Filter by type of service, price range, or ratings",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet3": "View detailed service provider profiles and reviews",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet4": "Book appointments and select preferred staff member",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet5": "Chat with providers before booking",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet6": "Pay securely through the app",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet7": "Receive appointment reminders",
  "docsGettingStartedForCustomers_customerFeaturesBullet8": "Rate and review services after completion",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq1Q": "What is Aura In?",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq1A": "Aura In is a mobile marketplace for service-based businesses. Customers find and book services (haircuts, massages, etc.), service providers manage bookings and revenue, and product sellers list items for sale.",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq2Q": "Do I need to pay to use the app?",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq2A": "The app is free to download and use. Service providers only pay a small commission when customers pay for services. Payment processors (Paystack/Stripe) take a fee.",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq3Q": "What is the difference between Shop Owner and Freelancer?",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq3A": "Shop owners have a fixed location with a team of workers. Freelancers work independently and can travel to clients. Choose based on your business model.",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq4Q": "How do I get paid?",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq4A": "When customers pay for services, money goes to your wallet. You can withdraw to your bank account using Paystack (Africa) or Stripe (Global).",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq5Q": "Is my payment information secure?",
  "docsGettingStartedFaq5A": "Yes. Aura In uses Paystack and Stripe, industry-leading payment processors with bank-level security. We never see your payment details.",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_title": "Getting Started with Your Shop",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_subtitle": "Learn the basics of creating your business profile",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_welcomeIntroTitle": "Welcome to Your Shop Dashboard",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_welcomeIntroContent": "Creating a shop on Aura In takes just a few minutes. You'll add your business information, set your services and working hours, and you're ready to accept bookings from customers.",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewTitle": "What You'll Set Up",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewContent": "Here's what you'll do when creating your shop:",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet1": "Add your shop name and logo",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet2": "Write a brief description of your business",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet3": "Choose your shop type (salon, barber, spa, etc.)",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet4": "Set your location and service address",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet5": "Add your working hours",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet6": "Create services you offer with pricing",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet7": "Add contact information",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_setupStepsOverviewBullet8": "Upload photos and documents",
  "docsCreateShopShopOverview_saveProgressTipContent": "Your work is saved automatically as you fill in the form. You can come back anytime to continue editing or publish when ready.",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_title": "Basic Shop Information",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_subtitle": "Tell customers who you are",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_logoSectionTitle": "Add Your Shop Logo",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_logoSectionContent": "Your logo is the first thing customers see. It should clearly represent your business. Use a square image (e.g., 500x500 pixels) for best results.",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopNameTitle": "Shop Name",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopNameContent": "Enter your business name exactly as you want customers to see it. Be clear and professional. Example: \"Marie's Hair Studio\" or \"City Barbershop\"",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeTitle": "Choose Your Shop Type",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeContent": "Select the type of business you run. This helps customers find you in search. Available types include:",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeBullet1": "Hair Salon - for haircuts, coloring, styling",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeBullet2": "Barber Shop - for men's haircuts and grooming",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeBullet3": "Spa - for massages, facials, wellness services",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeBullet4": "Beauty Services - makeup, nails, and other beauty treatments",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_shopTypeBullet5": "Other Services - for businesses not listed above",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_descriptionTitle": "Shop Description",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_descriptionContent": "Write a short description about your shop (100-200 words). Tell customers what makes you special. Example: \"We specialize in natural hair care and modern styling for all hair types. Family-friendly environment with professional stylists.\"",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_termsInfoTitle": "Terms & Conditions",
  "docsCreateShopBasicInfo_termsInfoContent": "Add any important rules customers should know. Examples: cancellation policy, age restrictions, deposit requirements, dress code, or health restrictions.",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_title": "Location & Hours",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_subtitle": "Where customers can find you and when you work",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_locationIntroTitle": "Set Your Location",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_locationIntroContent": "Customers need to know where to find you. You can either:",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_locationIntroBullet1": "Pin your location on the map (drag the marker)",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_locationIntroBullet2": "Search for your address in the search box",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_locationIntroBullet3": "Enter your street address manually",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_locationAccuracyContent": "Make sure your location is accurate. Customers use it to find you and calculate travel time.",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_workingHoursTitle": "Set Your Working Hours",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_workingHoursContent": "Customers can only book times when you're open. Set your hours for each day of the week.",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_hoursExampleTitle": "Example Hours",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_hoursExampleContent": "Monday - Friday: 9:00 AM to 6:00 PM\nSaturday: 9:00 AM to 5:00 PM\nSunday: Closed",
  "docsCreateShopLocationSetup_hoursTipContent": "You can set different hours for different days, or mark any day as closed when you're not working.",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_title": "Services & Pricing",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_subtitle": "Tell customers what you offer and how much it costs",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_servicesIntroTitle": "Add Your Services",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_servicesIntroContent": "Each service is something customers can book and pay for. Examples: \"Haircut\", \"Hair Color\", \"Massage\", \"Facial Treatment\".",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsTitle": "For Each Service, Add:",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsContent": "When you create a service, you need to provide:",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsBullet1": "Service name - what you're offering (e.g., \"Haircut\")",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsBullet2": "Description - brief details about what's included",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsBullet3": "Price - how much the service costs",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsBullet4": "Duration - how long it takes (e.g., 30 minutes, 1 hour)",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_serviceDetailsBullet5": "Category - what type of service it is",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_pricingTipTitle": "Pricing Tip",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_pricingTipContent": "Be clear with your prices. You can offer different service tiers (e.g., \"Basic Haircut\" vs \"Premium Haircut\") at different prices.",
  "docsCreateShopServicesSetup_durationImportantContent": "Set the duration accurately. Customers book based on this time, and staff need to know how long to reserve.",
  "docsCreateShopFaq1Q": "How long does it take to create a shop?",
  "docsCreateShopFaq1A": "Most businesses can set up a shop in 5-15 minutes. You just need your business name, location, at least one service, and working hours.",
  "docsCreateShopFaq2Q": "What do I need to start?",
  "docsCreateShopFaq2A": "You need: your business name, location address, shop type, at least one service with pricing, and your working hours. A logo and photos are optional but recommended.",
  "docsCreateShopFaq3Q": "Can I change things after publishing?",
  "docsCreateShopFaq3A": "Yes! You can edit everything after your shop is live. Go to \"My Shops\", click on your shop, and click \"Edit\". All changes take effect immediately.",
  "docsCreateShopFaq4Q": "Do I need team members to start?",
  "docsCreateShopFaq4A": "No. If you're a solo business, you can start immediately. You can add team members anytime from your shop settings.",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_title": "Getting Started as a Freelancer",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_subtitle": "Learn how to set up your profile and start taking clients",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerWelcomeTitle": "Welcome to Freelancing",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerWelcomeContent": "As a freelancer on Aura In, you offer services directly to customers in your area. Unlike a traditional shop, you work from your own location and can travel to meet clients. Set up your profile in just a few minutes and start accepting bookings.",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopTitle": "Freelancer vs Shop: What's the Difference?",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopContent": "Here's how freelancing works:",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopBullet1": "You work independently - no fixed storefront required",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopBullet2": "You can travel to clients within your chosen radius",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopBullet3": "You set your own hours and availability",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopBullet4": "You manage your own schedule and clients",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerVsShopBullet5": "Customers book you directly for services",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerRequirementsTitle": "What You'll Need",
  "docsFreelancerFreelancerOverview_freelancerRequirementsContent": "To start as a freelancer, you need: your name, a profession type (hairdresser, massage therapist, etc.), location, travel radius, services, and your working hours. A professional photo helps customers trust you.",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_title": "Create Your Profile",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_subtitle": "Tell customers who you are",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_profilePhotoTitle": "Add Your Profile Photo",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_profilePhotoContent": "A professional headshot or portrait builds trust with customers. Use a clear, well-lit photo of yourself. Customers want to know who they're booking with.",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_yourNameTitle": "Your Name",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_yourNameContent": "Enter your full name exactly as you want customers to see it. Be professional and clear.",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_professionTypeTitle": "Choose Your Profession",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_professionTypeContent": "Select what you do. Examples: Hairdresser, Massage Therapist, Makeup Artist, Barber, Esthetician, or other specialized services.",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_bioDescriptionTitle": "Write Your Bio",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_bioDescriptionContent": "Write a short description about yourself and your experience (50-150 words). Tell customers what makes you unique. Example: \"I specialize in natural hair care with 5 years of experience. Certified in color and styling.\"",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_termsGuidelinesTitle": "Add Your Guidelines",
  "docsFreelancerProfileSetup_termsGuidelinesContent": "Share any important rules or policies. Examples: age restrictions, cancellation policy, health requirements, or preparation instructions.",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_title": "Set Your Service Area",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_subtitle": "Define where you work",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_baseLocationTitle": "Set Your Base Location",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_baseLocationContent": "This is where you normally work from. Customers within your travel radius can book you. You can either pin on the map or search for your address.",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_travelRadiusTitle": "Travel Radius",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_travelRadiusContent": "How far are you willing to travel to meet clients? Set this in kilometers. Example: \"5 km radius\" means clients up to 5 km from your location can book you.",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_mobileVsFixedTitle": "Mobile or Fixed Location?",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_mobileVsFixedContent": "Choose whether you travel to clients or meet them at one location. If you're mobile, customers can request you at their home or office.",
  "docsFreelancerServiceArea_serviceAddressTipContent": "Customers will see your travel radius when searching. Be accurate so they know if you can serve their area.",
  "docsFreelancerFaq1Q": "What's the difference between a freelancer and a shop owner?",
  "docsFreelancerFaq1A": "A freelancer works independently, often traveling to clients. A shop owner has a fixed location. Freelancers are more flexible, shops are more established.",
  "docsFreelancerFaq2Q": "How do customers find me?",
  "docsFreelancerFaq2A": "Your profile appears in customer searches based on your location, profession, and services. A good photo and portfolio help you get found more.",
  "docsFreelancerFaq3Q": "Can I work for multiple platforms?",
  "docsFreelancerFaq3A": "Yes! You can set up profiles on multiple platforms. Just make sure your availability matches across all platforms.",
  "docsFreelancerFaq4Q": "How do payments work?",
  "docsFreelancerFaq4A": "Customers pay through the app. You receive payment to your account after the service is completed.",
  "docsFreelancerFaq5Q": "What if I need to cancel a booking?",
  "docsFreelancerFaq5A": "You can cancel before the booking time. Contact support if you need to reschedule. Be fair to customers - frequent cancellations hurt your rating.",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_title": "Welcome to the Booking System",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_subtitle": "Everything you need to know about booking services, whether you're a client or a shop owner.",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whatIsBooking_title": "What is the Booking System?",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whatIsBooking_content": "The booking system is your gateway to scheduling services at your favorite shops. Whether you need a haircut, beard trim, braiding, or any other service, the system makes it easy to book appointments at your convenience.",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whoItsFor_title": "Who is this guide for?",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whoItsFor_content": "This guide is designed for two types of users:",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whoItsFor_bullet1": "Clients: People who want to book services at shops",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whoItsFor_bullet2": "Guest Bookers: People who want to book via a link without creating an account",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_whoItsFor_bullet3": "Shop Owners: People who manage shops, services, and workers",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_guestBookingIntro_title": "New: Book Without Downloading the App",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_guestBookingIntro_content": "No account? No problem! If a shop owner shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without downloading the app. Your receipt is sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsBookingStartedBookingIntro_welcomeNote_content": "No technical knowledge needed! This guide uses simple language and real examples to help you understand everything.",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_title": "Creating Your Account (Or Booking as Guest)",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_subtitle": "Get started in minutes - with or without an account",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_twoWaysToBook_title": "Two Ways to Book",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_twoWaysToBook_content": "You can book in two ways:",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_twoWaysToBook_bullet1": "With Account: Download app, create account, book anytime",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_twoWaysToBook_bullet2": "As Guest: Use booking link, no app needed, receipt via WhatsApp",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_title": "How to Create an Account",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_content": "Follow these simple steps to create your account:",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_bullet1": "Download the app from App Store or Google Play",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_bullet2": "Tap \"Sign Up\" on the welcome screen",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_bullet3": "Enter your email address and create a password",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_bullet4": "Add your name and profile picture (optional)",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_bullet5": "Verify your email address",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountSteps_bullet6": "You're ready to start booking!",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountTypes_title": "Account Types",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountTypes_content": "There are two types of accounts:",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountTypes_bullet1": "Client Account: For booking services at shops",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_accountTypes_bullet2": "Shop Owner Account: For managing your own shop (requires approval)",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_guestBookingOption_title": "Booking as a Guest (No Account)",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_guestBookingOption_content": "If someone shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without creating an account. Just click the link and follow the steps. Your receipt is sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsBookingStartedCreatingAccount_verificationNote_content": "You can browse and book without an account using a booking link. Creating an account gives you access to booking history, saved payments, and loyalty rewards.",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_title": "Your First Booking",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_subtitle": "A quick walkthrough",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_title": "How to make your first booking",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_content": "Here's what you'll do:",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_bullet1": "Find a shop you like",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_bullet2": "Browse their services",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_bullet3": "Select the services you want",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_bullet4": "Choose your preferred worker (if available)",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_bullet5": "Pick a date and time",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingSteps_bullet6": "Review and confirm your booking",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_title": "What happens after you book?",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_content": "Once you confirm your booking:",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_bullet1": "You'll get an instant confirmation",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_bullet2": "The booking appears in \"My Bookings\"",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_bullet3": "You'll receive a reminder before your appointment",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_bullet4": "The shop gets notified of your booking",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_whatHappensNext_bullet5": "You can reschedule or cancel if plans change",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_title": "How Payment Works",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_content": "When you book a service, here's how payment works:",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_bullet1": "30% Deposit Required: To secure your booking, you pay 30% of the total service cost upfront",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_bullet2": "Platform Fee: A small fixed fee (e.g., GHS 2) is added to help maintain the platform",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_bullet3": "Non-Refundable: Deposit and fee are non-refundable if you cancel or don't show up",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_bullet4": "Remaining 70%: Paid after service - either in cash or via app",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_paymentProcess_bullet5": "Secure Payment: All payments are processed securely through our payment partners",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_remainingPaymentOptions_title": "Flexible Payment for Remaining Balance",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_remainingPaymentOptions_content": "After your service, you have options for paying the remaining 70%:",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_remainingPaymentOptions_bullet1": "Pay in Cash: Hand cash directly to worker or shop counter",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_remainingPaymentOptions_bullet2": "Pay via App: Use card, mobile money, or digital payment through the app",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_remainingPaymentOptions_bullet3": "You choose: Either option is available at the time of service",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_depositNote_content": "The 30% deposit protects both you and the shop. It ensures your slot is reserved exclusively for you, and compensates the worker if you cancel last minute. The platform fee helps us maintain secure payments and customer support.",
  "docsBookingStartedFirstBooking_bookingTip_content": "Pro tip: Book at least 24 hours in advance for the best selection of time slots, especially for popular services.",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_title": "Finding Your Way Around",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_subtitle": "Key screens and what they do",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_title": "Main Screens",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_content": "The app has several key screens to help you navigate:",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_bullet1": "Home: Discover shops and services near you",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_bullet2": "Search: Find specific shops or services",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_bullet3": "My Bookings: View and manage your appointments",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_bullet4": "Profile: Your account settings and preferences",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_mainScreens_bullet5": "Favorites: Save shops you love for quick access",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_bookingFlow_title": "The Booking Flow",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_bookingFlow_content": "When you start booking, you'll go through these steps:",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_bookingFlow_bullet1": "Services: Choose what you want",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_bookingFlow_bullet2": "Workers: Pick who you want (if applicable)",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_bookingFlow_bullet3": "Time: Select your preferred date and time",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_bookingFlow_bullet4": "Confirm: Review and finalize your booking",
  "docsBookingStartedNavigation_navigationTip_content": "You can always go back to previous steps using the back button. Your selections are saved as you move through the flow.",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_title": "Booking Basics",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_subtitle": "Key concepts explained simply",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_title": "Important Terms to Know",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_content": "Here are some terms you'll encounter:",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_bullet1": "Service: What you want done (haircut, braids, etc.)",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_bullet2": "Worker: The person who performs the service",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_bullet3": "Slot: A specific date and time for your appointment",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_bullet4": "Group Booking: Booking for multiple people at once",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_keyTerms_bullet5": "Buffer Time: Clean-up time between appointments (you won't see this)",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_whatYouNeed_title": "What You Need Before Booking",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_whatYouNeed_content": "Before you start, have this information ready:",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_whatYouNeed_bullet1": "The service you want",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_whatYouNeed_bullet2": "Preferred date and time (flexibility helps!)",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_whatYouNeed_bullet3": "Number of people (if booking for a group)",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_whatYouNeed_bullet4": "Worker preference (if you have one)",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_depositExplained_title": "Understanding the Deposit",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_depositExplained_content": "Here's a real example of how the deposit works:",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_depositExample_title": "Example",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_depositExample_content": "Sarah books a haircut that costs GHS 100.\n• At booking: She pays GHS 30 (30% deposit)\n• After service: She pays GHS 70 (remaining balance)\n• Total paid: GHS 100\n\nIf Sarah cancels: She loses the GHS 30 deposit, but isn't charged the remaining GHS 70.\n\nIf Sarah doesn't show up: Same as cancellation - the GHS 30 deposit is kept.",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_depositTip_content": "The deposit is applied toward your total bill. You're not paying extra - you're just paying part of it upfront to secure your spot.",
  "docsBookingStartedBasics_basicsImportant_content": "All times shown in the app are in your local timezone. No need to worry about timezone conversions!",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq1Q": "Can I book without an account?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq1A": "You can browse shops and services without an account, but you'll need to sign up to actually book appointments. This helps us keep track of your bookings and send you reminders.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq2Q": "Does it cost anything to use the booking system?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq2A": "The booking system is completely free for clients. You only pay for the services you book. Shop owners pay a small commission on each booking.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq3Q": "Can I book at multiple shops at the same time?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq3A": "Yes! You can book appointments at different shops. Just make sure the times don't overlap if you're planning to attend them all yourself.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq4Q": "Is the deposit refundable if I cancel?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq4A": "No, the 30% deposit is non-refundable. This policy helps shops protect their time in case of last-minute cancellations or no-shows. You can cancel up to 24 hours before your appointment to avoid being charged the remaining 70%, but the deposit will not be refunded.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq5Q": "Why 30%? Why not a fixed amount?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq5A": "The 30% deposit scales with the cost of your service. For expensive services, the deposit is higher (protecting the shop more), and for cheaper services, it's lower (fairer for you). This percentage was chosen as a balanced approach that works for both clients and shops.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq6Q": "If I book multiple services, do I pay 30% of the total?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq6A": "Yes! The 30% deposit is calculated based on the total cost of all services you're booking. So if your total is GHS 200, you'll pay GHS 60 upfront, and the remaining GHS 140 after your appointment.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq7Q": "What if I have a genuine emergency?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq7A": "We understand that emergencies happen. While the deposit is officially non-refundable, you can contact the shop directly through the app to explain your situation. Some shops may offer credit toward a future booking at their discretion.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq8Q": "Will I get reminders about my booking?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq8A": "Yes! You'll receive reminders 24 hours before your appointment and again 1 hour before. You can adjust reminder settings in your profile.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq9Q": "When do I pay for my booking?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq9A": "Payment is handled at the time of booking. You can pay using credit card, debit card, or other payment methods available in your region.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq10Q": "I own a shop. How do I get started?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq10A": "Great! Create an account and select \"Shop Owner\" during signup. You'll need to provide some information about your shop and wait for approval. Once approved, you can start adding services and workers.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq11Q": "Can I book without creating an account?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq11A": "Yes! If a shop owner shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without an account. Just click the link and follow the booking steps. Your receipt is sent to your WhatsApp. You can create an account later if you want to track all your bookings in one place.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq12Q": "What is the platform fee and why do I pay it?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq12A": "The platform fee is a small fixed charge (e.g., GHS 2) added to your booking. It helps us maintain the app, process payments securely, provide customer support, and develop new features. Only one platform fee per booking, even for multiple services or people.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq13Q": "Can I pay the remaining 70% in cash?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq13A": "Yes! You have flexibility. You can pay the remaining 70% either in cash directly to the shop/worker, or through the app using your preferred payment method. The choice is yours at the time of service.",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq14Q": "As a guest, how do I get my booking details?",
  "docsBookingStartedFaq14A": "Your booking confirmation and receipt are sent to your WhatsApp number. You'll receive appointment reminders and can track everything through WhatsApp without downloading the app.",
  "docsHowBooktitle": "How to Book Services",
  "docsHowBooksubtitle": "How to Book Services",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_title": "Booking at a Glance",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_subtitle": "The booking process in simple steps",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_twoBookingWays_title": "Two Ways to Book",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_twoBookingWays_content": "You can book in two ways:",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_twoBookingWays_bullet1": "**With App Account:** Download app, create account, book anytime",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_twoBookingWays_bullet2": "**As Guest:** Use booking link, no app needed, receipt via WhatsApp",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_title": "Your Booking Journey (With Account)",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_content": "Booking a service takes just a few minutes. Here's what you'll do:",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_bullet1": "**Step 1:** Find a shop and browse services",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_bullet2": "**Step 2:** Select your services and quantities",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_bullet3": "**Step 3:** Choose your preferred worker (if available)",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_bullet4": "**Step 4:** Pick a date and time",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_bullet5": "**Step 5:** Pay 30% deposit + small fee to confirm",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingStepsOverview_bullet6": "**Step 6:** After service, pay remaining 70% in cash or via app",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_guestBookingNote_title": "Guest Booking (No App)",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_guestBookingNote_content": "Don't have the app? If a shop shares a booking link with you, follow the same steps above but without needing to create an account. Your confirmation and receipt go to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsHowBookBookingOverview_bookingTimeNote_content": "The entire process usually takes less than 2 minutes. Your progress is saved as you go, so you can take your time.",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_title": "Step 1: Find Your Shop & Services",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_subtitle": "Discover the perfect place for your needs",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_findShop_title": "How to find a shop",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_findShop_content": "You can find shops in several ways:",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_findShop_bullet1": "**Home Screen:** Browse recommended shops near you",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_findShop_bullet2": "**Search:** Look for specific shops or services by name",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_findShop_bullet3": "**Categories:** Filter by service type (Haircut, Braiding, Beard, etc.)",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_findShop_bullet4": "**Favorites:** Quick access to shops you've saved",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_title": "Browsing Services",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_content": "Once you select a shop, you'll see all their available services. Each service shows:",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_bullet1": "**Service name** (e.g., \"Afro Haircut\", \"Box Braids\")",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_bullet2": "**Duration** (how long it takes)",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_bullet3": "**Price** (cost of the service - this goes to the shop)",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_bullet4": "**Description** (what's included)",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_browseServices_bullet5": "**Worker requirement** (whether you can choose who does it)",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_serviceExample_title": "Example",
  "docsHowBookStepOne_serviceExample_content": "**Haircut Service:**\n• Name: Afro Haircut\n• Duration: 1 hour\n• Price: GHS 45 (paid to shop)\n• Description: Professional afro haircut with styling\n• Worker: You can choose your preferred barber",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_title": "Step 2: Select Your Services",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_subtitle": "Choose what you want and how many people",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_selectServices_title": "Selecting Services",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_selectServices_content": "To select a service, simply tap on it. You'll see it become highlighted. You can select multiple services at once:",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_selectServices_bullet1": "Tap a service to select it",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_selectServices_bullet2": "Selected services show a checkmark",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_selectServices_bullet3": "You can select multiple services (e.g., Haircut + Beard Trim)",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_selectServices_bullet4": "Tap again to deselect",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupBooking_title": "Booking for Multiple People",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupBooking_content": "If you're booking for a group (like yourself and your children), you can increase the quantity:",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupBooking_bullet1": "After selecting a service, you'll see a **+** and **-** button",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupBooking_bullet2": "Tap **+** to increase the number of people",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupBooking_bullet3": "The price updates automatically",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupBooking_bullet4": "Maximum quantity is shown (some services have limits)",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupExample_title": "Example: Family Booking",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_groupExample_content": "**Dad wants haircuts for himself and his two sons:**\n• Select \"Haircut\" service\n• Tap **+** until quantity shows 3\n• Total price shows 3 × GHS 45 = GHS 135 (for the shop)\n• You'll choose workers for each person later",
  "docsHowBookStepTwo_quantityTip_content": "The quantity feature is perfect for families, groups of friends, or anyone booking for multiple people at once.",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_title": "Step 3: Choose Your Workers",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_subtitle": "Pick who will perform your services",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerSelection_title": "When You Can Choose a Worker",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerSelection_content": "Some services let you choose your preferred worker, while others assign whoever is available:",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerSelection_bullet1": "**Services with worker choice:** You'll see a \"Choose Worker\" button",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerSelection_bullet2": "**Services without worker choice:** The system will assign an available worker",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerSelection_bullet3": "**Group bookings:** You can choose different workers for each person",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_title": "How to Choose a Worker",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_content": "If a service lets you choose a worker:",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_bullet1": "Tap \"Choose Worker\" for that service",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_bullet2": "You'll see a list of available workers",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_bullet3": "Each worker shows their name, photo, specialties, and rating",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_bullet4": "Tap on a worker to select them",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_choosingWorker_bullet5": "For group bookings, you'll choose a worker for each person",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerExample_title": "Example: Group with Different Workers",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerExample_content": "**Family of 3 booking haircuts:**\n• Person 1 (Dad): Choose John (fade specialist)\n• Person 2 (Son 1): Choose Michael (kids cuts)\n• Person 3 (Son 2): Choose Michael (same worker)\n• All three will be served during your appointment time",
  "docsHowBookStepThree_workerTip_content": "You can see each worker's availability in real-time. If your preferred worker isn't available at your desired time, you'll need to choose a different time or worker.",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_title": "Step 4: Pick Your Date & Time",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_subtitle": "Select when you want your appointment",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_dateSelection_title": "Choosing a Date",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_dateSelection_content": "First, pick your preferred date from the calendar:",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_dateSelection_bullet1": "Dates with available slots are highlighted",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_dateSelection_bullet2": "Past dates are greyed out",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_dateSelection_bullet3": "Today is marked with \"Today\"",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_dateSelection_bullet4": "You can scroll forward up to 30 days",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_timeSelection_title": "Two Ways to View Time Slots",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_timeSelection_content": "Once you pick a date, you'll see available time slots. You can switch between two views:",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_timeSelection_bullet1": "**Regular View:** Shows slots for each service separately",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_timeSelection_bullet2": "**Combined View:** Shows only slots where ALL your services can be booked together",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_regularVsCombined_title": "Regular vs Combined View",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_regularVsCombined_content": "**Regular View Example (2 services):**\n• Haircut: 9:00 AM, 9:30 AM, 10:00 AM...\n• Beard Trim: 9:00 AM, 9:30 AM, 10:00 AM...\n\n**Combined View Example (same 2 services):**\n• 9:00 AM - 10:30 AM (both services together)\n• 9:30 AM - 11:00 AM\n• 10:00 AM - 11:30 AM",
  "docsHowBookStepFour_viewSwitch_content": "Use the toggle switch to switch between Regular and Combined view. Combined view is especially useful when booking multiple services.",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_title": "Step 5: Payment & Confirmation",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_subtitle": "Secure your booking with a 30% deposit",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_title": "How Payment Works",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_content": "To secure your booking, you'll pay a 30% deposit plus a small processing fee. Here's what you need to know:",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_bullet1": "**30% Deposit:** Required at the time of booking (goes to the shop)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_bullet2": "**Processing Fee:** Small fixed fee charged by the platform (e.g., GHS 2 per booking)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_bullet3": "**Non-Refundable Deposit:** The 30% deposit is not refunded if you cancel or don't show up",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_bullet4": "**Processing Fee Non-Refundable:** The platform fee is also non-refundable",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentOverview_bullet5": "**Secure Processing:** All payments are encrypted and secure",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentExample_title": "Payment Example",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentExample_content": "**Sarah books services totaling GHS 200:**\n• At booking: Pays GHS 60 (30% deposit for shop) + GHS 2 (platform fee) = GHS 62\n• After service: Pays remaining GHS 140 to the shop (in cash or via app)\n• Total paid: GHS 200 to shop + GHS 2 platform fee\n\n**If Sarah cancels:** She loses the GHS 60 deposit and GHS 2 fee\n**If Sarah doesn't show up:** Same as cancellation",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_title": "The Payment Screen",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_content": "On the confirmation screen, you'll see:",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet1": "**Summary:** All services, quantities, and workers",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet2": "**Total Price:** Full cost of all services (for the shop)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet3": "**Deposit Amount:** 30% payable now",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet4": "**Platform Fee:** Small processing fee (e.g., GHS 2)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet5": "**Total Due Now:** Deposit + platform fee",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet6": "**Remaining Balance:** 70% to pay after service (cash or app)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentStep_bullet7": "**Payment Methods:** Choose how to pay the deposit",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_feeExplanation_title": "Understanding the Platform Fee",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_feeExplanation_content": "The processing fee (e.g., GHS 2 per booking) is charged by the platform, not the shop. This fee helps us maintain the app and provide you with a great booking experience. The fee is:",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_feeExplanation_bullet1": "**Fixed amount** (not a percentage)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_feeExplanation_bullet2": "**Charged once per booking** (not per service)",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_feeExplanation_bullet3": "**Non-refundable** even if you cancel",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_feeExplanation_bullet4": "**Clearly shown** before you confirm",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentImportant_content": "The 30% deposit goes to the shop and is applied toward your total bill. The platform fee is separate and helps keep the app running. You're not paying extra to the shop - just paying part of your bill upfront.",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_remainingPayment_title": "Paying the Remaining 70%",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_remainingPayment_content": "After your service is complete, you have two options to pay the remaining balance:",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_remainingPayment_bullet1": "**Cash:** Pay the worker or shop directly",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_remainingPayment_bullet2": "**Via App:** Pay through the app using your preferred payment method",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_remainingPayment_bullet3": "**Receipt:** You'll get a receipt regardless of how you pay",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_title": "After Payment",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_content": "Once your deposit payment is successful:",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_bullet1": "You'll see a confirmation screen",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_bullet2": "The booking appears in \"My Bookings\"",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_bullet3": "You'll receive an email confirmation",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_bullet4": "The shop is notified of your booking",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_confirmation_bullet5": "You'll get a reminder before your appointment",
  "docsHowBookStepFive_paymentWarning_content": "The 30% deposit and platform fee are non-refundable. Please be sure about your booking before confirming. You can reschedule up to 24 hours before, but the deposit and fee remain non-refundable.",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_title": "After You Book",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_subtitle": "What happens next",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_title": "Your Booking is Confirmed!",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_content": "Here's what you can do after booking:",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_bullet1": "**View Booking:** Check details in \"My Bookings\"",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_bullet2": "**Reschedule:** Change the time (up to 24 hours before)",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_bullet3": "**Cancel:** Cancel if needed (deposit and fee are non-refundable)",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_bullet4": "**Contact Shop:** Message the shop directly",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_whatsNext_bullet5": "**Add to Calendar:** Export to your phone's calendar",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_reminders_title": "Booking Reminders",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_reminders_content": "You'll receive reminders at:",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_reminders_bullet1": "**24 hours before:** Check you're still coming",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_reminders_bullet2": "**1 hour before:** Time to head to the shop",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_reminders_bullet3": "**After appointment:** Option to leave a review and pay remaining balance",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterService_title": "After Your Service",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterService_content": "Once your service is complete:",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterService_bullet1": "**Pay Remaining 70%:** In cash or through the app",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterService_bullet2": "**Rate Your Experience:** Leave a review for the shop and worker",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterService_bullet3": "**Tip Your Worker:** Optional tip can be added",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterService_bullet4": "**Book Again:** Easily rebook with the same shop or worker",
  "docsHowBookAfterBooking_afterTip_content": "Arrive 5-10 minutes before your appointment time to check in. This gives you time to settle in before your service starts.",
  "docsHowBookFaq11": "How do I cancel a booking?",
  "docsHowBookFaq21": "Go to \"My Bookings\", find the booking, and tap \"Cancel\". You can cancel up to 24 hours before the appointment. The 30% deposit and platform fee are non-refundable, but you won't be charged the remaining 70%.",
  "docsHowBookFaq32": "Can I change my appointment time?",
  "docsHowBookFaq42": "Yes! Go to \"My Bookings\", find your booking, and tap \"Reschedule\". You can choose a new time if available. The deposit and fee remain applied to your new booking.",
  "docsHowBookFaq53": "Why do I need to pay a deposit?",
  "docsHowBookFaq63": "The 30% deposit protects both you and the shop. It ensures your slot is reserved exclusively for you, and compensates the worker if you cancel last minute. The deposit goes toward your total bill.",
  "docsHowBookFaq74": "What is the platform fee?",
  "docsHowBookFaq84": "The platform fee (e.g., GHS 2 per booking) is a small fixed charge by the app, not the shop. It helps us maintain the platform and provide you with a smooth booking experience. The fee is clearly shown before you confirm.",
  "docsHowBookFaq95": "Is the deposit ever refundable?",
  "docsHowBookFaq105": "The deposit and platform fee are non-refundable by policy. However, in genuine emergency situations, you can contact the shop directly through the app. Some shops may offer credit toward a future booking at their discretion, but the platform fee cannot be refunded.",
  "docsHowBookFaq116": "How do I pay the remaining 70%?",
  "docsHowBookFaq126": "After your service, you have two options: pay in cash directly to the shop, or pay through the app using your preferred payment method. Both options are accepted at participating shops.",
  "docsHowBookFaq137": "Can I book multiple services at once?",
  "docsHowBookFaq147": "Absolutely! You can select multiple services (like haircut + beard trim) and book them together. The system will find time slots where all services can be done.",
  "docsHowBookFaq158": "How do I book for multiple people?",
  "docsHowBookFaq168": "After selecting a service, use the **+** button to increase the quantity. For example, if you're booking haircuts for yourself and two children, set quantity to 3. You can then choose different workers for each person.",
  "docsHowBookFaq179": "Can I change my chosen worker after booking?",
  "docsHowBookFaq189": "Yes, you can change your worker up to 24 hours before the appointment. Go to \"My Bookings\", find your booking, and look for the option to change worker. The new worker must be available at your booked time.",
  "docsHowBookFaq191": "What payment methods are accepted for the deposit?",
  "docsHowBookFaq201": "We accept various payment methods depending on your region, including credit/debit cards, mobile money, and bank transfers. Available options will be shown during checkout.",
  "docsHowBookFaq211": "When should I use Combined View?",
  "docsHowBookFaq221": "Use Combined View when you've selected multiple services. It shows only time slots where all your services can be done together, saving you from trying to coordinate separate times.",
  "docsHowBookFaq231": "What happens if I don't show up?",
  "docsHowBookFaq241": "If you don't show up for your appointment, the 30% deposit and platform fee are kept. You may also be marked as a \"no-show\". Repeated no-shows may result in restrictions on your account.",
  "docsHowBookFaq251": "Can I really pay the remaining amount in cash?",
  "docsHowBookFaq261": "Yes! Many shops accept cash for the remaining 70%. You can also choose to pay through the app if you prefer. The choice is yours at the time of service.",
  "docsHowBookFaq271": "Is the platform fee charged per service or per booking?",
  "docsHowBookFaq281": "The platform fee is charged **per booking**, not per service. So whether you book one service or multiple services together, you pay the platform fee only once.",
  "docsHowBookFaq291": "Can I book without creating an account?",
  "docsHowBookFaq301": "Yes! If a shop shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without an account or downloading the app. Follow the same booking steps, and your confirmation and receipt are sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsHowBookFaq1Q": "How do I cancel a booking?",
  "docsHowBookFaq1A": "Go to \"My Bookings\", find the booking, and tap \"Cancel\". You can cancel up to 24 hours before the appointment. The 30% deposit and platform fee are non-refundable, but you won't be charged the remaining 70%.",
  "docsHowBookFaq2Q": "Can I change my appointment time?",
  "docsHowBookFaq2A": "Yes! Go to \"My Bookings\", find your booking, and tap \"Reschedule\". You can choose a new time if available. The deposit and fee remain applied to your new booking.",
  "docsHowBookFaq3Q": "Why do I need to pay a deposit?",
  "docsHowBookFaq3A": "The 30% deposit protects both you and the shop. It ensures your slot is reserved exclusively for you, and compensates the worker if you cancel last minute. The deposit goes toward your total bill.",
  "docsHowBookFaq4Q": "What is the platform fee?",
  "docsHowBookFaq4A": "The platform fee (e.g., GHS 2 per booking) is a small fixed charge by the app, not the shop. It helps us maintain the platform and provide you with a smooth booking experience. The fee is clearly shown before you confirm.",
  "docsHowBookFaq5Q": "Is the deposit ever refundable?",
  "docsHowBookFaq5A": "The deposit and platform fee are non-refundable by policy. However, in genuine emergency situations, you can contact the shop directly through the app. Some shops may offer credit toward a future booking at their discretion, but the platform fee cannot be refunded.",
  "docsHowBookFaq6Q": "How do I pay the remaining 70%?",
  "docsHowBookFaq6A": "After your service, you have two options: pay in cash directly to the shop, or pay through the app using your preferred payment method. Both options are accepted at participating shops.",
  "docsHowBookFaq7Q": "Can I book multiple services at once?",
  "docsHowBookFaq7A": "Absolutely! You can select multiple services (like haircut + beard trim) and book them together. The system will find time slots where all services can be done.",
  "docsHowBookFaq8Q": "How do I book for multiple people?",
  "docsHowBookFaq8A": "After selecting a service, use the **+** button to increase the quantity. For example, if you're booking haircuts for yourself and two children, set quantity to 3. You can then choose different workers for each person.",
  "docsHowBookFaq9Q": "Can I change my chosen worker after booking?",
  "docsHowBookFaq9A": "Yes, you can change your worker up to 24 hours before the appointment. Go to \"My Bookings\", find your booking, and look for the option to change worker. The new worker must be available at your booked time.",
  "docsHowBookFaq10Q": "What payment methods are accepted for the deposit?",
  "docsHowBookFaq10A": "We accept various payment methods depending on your region, including credit/debit cards, mobile money, and bank transfers. Available options will be shown during checkout.",
  "docsHowBookFaq11Q": "When should I use Combined View?",
  "docsHowBookFaq11A": "Use Combined View when you've selected multiple services. It shows only time slots where all your services can be done together, saving you from trying to coordinate separate times.",
  "docsHowBookFaq12Q": "What happens if I don't show up?",
  "docsHowBookFaq12A": "If you don't show up for your appointment, the 30% deposit and platform fee are kept. You may also be marked as a \"no-show\". Repeated no-shows may result in restrictions on your account.",
  "docsHowBookFaq13Q": "Can I really pay the remaining amount in cash?",
  "docsHowBookFaq13A": "Yes! Many shops accept cash for the remaining 70%. You can also choose to pay through the app if you prefer. The choice is yours at the time of service.",
  "docsHowBookFaq14Q": "Is the platform fee charged per service or per booking?",
  "docsHowBookFaq14A": "The platform fee is charged **per booking**, not per service. So whether you book one service or multiple services together, you pay the platform fee only once.",
  "docsHowBookFaq15Q": "Can I book without creating an account?",
  "docsHowBookFaq15A": "Yes! If a shop shares a booking link with you, you can book directly without an account or downloading the app. Follow the same booking steps, and your confirmation and receipt are sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_title": "What Are Group Bookings?",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_subtitle": "Booking for family, friends, or groups made simple",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_title": "How to Make a Group Booking",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_subtitle": "Step-by-step guide",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_title": "Worker Selection for Groups",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_subtitle": "How workers are assigned",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_title": "Time Slots for Groups",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_subtitle": "How appointment times work for groups",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_title": "Payment for Group Bookings",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_subtitle": "How deposits and fees work",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_title": "Common Group Scenarios",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_subtitle": "Real examples to help you understand",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_explained_title": "Booking for Multiple People",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_explained_content": "Group bookings allow you to book services for more than one person at a time. This is perfect for:",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_explained_bullet1": "**Families:** Parents booking haircuts for themselves and their children",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_explained_bullet2": "**Friends:** Group of friends getting services together",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_explained_bullet3": "**Events:** Bridal parties, birthdays, or special occasions",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_explained_bullet4": "**Colleagues:** Team building or work outings",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_example_title": "Real-Life Example",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_example_content": "**The Mensah Family needs haircuts:**\n• Father: Wants a fade haircut\n• Mother: Wants a trim\n• Son (10): Wants a kids haircut\n• Daughter (8): Wants braids\n\nInstead of making 4 separate bookings, they can book everything together in one go!",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_title": "Benefits of Group Booking",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_content": "Booking as a group gives you:",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_bullet1": "**One transaction:** Pay deposits for everyone at once",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_bullet2": "**Coordinated timing:** Everyone gets served around the same time",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_bullet3": "**Different workers:** Each person can choose their preferred worker",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_bullet4": "**Simplified management:** View and manage all bookings together",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_benefits_bullet5": "**Better planning:** Shop can prepare for your group",
  "docsGroupBookingsIntro_tip_content": "Group bookings are perfect for families! You can book for yourself and your children in one go, choosing different workers for each person. No account needed? Use a booking link shared by the shop!",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step1_title": "Step 1: Select Your Service",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step1_content": "Start by finding a shop and selecting the service you want. For example, tap on \"Haircut\".",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2_title": "Step 2: Choose the Quantity",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2_content": "After selecting a service, you'll see **+** and **-** buttons. Use these to set how many people need this service:",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2_bullet1": "Tap **+** to increase the number",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2_bullet2": "Tap **-** to decrease",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2_bullet3": "The price updates automatically",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2_bullet4": "You cannot exceed the maximum quantity shown",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2Example_title": "Example",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step2Example_content": "**For a family of 3 needing haircuts:**\n• Select \"Haircut\" service\n• Tap **+** twice (or until quantity shows 3)\n• Total price shows: 3 × GHS 45 = GHS 135",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3_title": "Step 3: Repeat for Each Service",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3_content": "If your group needs different services (e.g., some want haircuts, others want braids), select each service and set the quantity for each:",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3_bullet1": "Select \"Haircut\" → set quantity 2",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3_bullet2": "Select \"Braids\" → set quantity 1",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3_bullet3": "The system keeps track of all selections",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3Example_title": "Example: Mixed Services",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step3Example_content": "**Family of 4 with different needs:**\n• Dad: Haircut (quantity 1)\n• Mom: Trim (quantity 1)\n• Son: Kids Haircut (quantity 1)\n• Daughter: Braids (quantity 1)\n\nTotal: 4 services, but you booked them all in one go!",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4_title": "Step 4: Choose Workers for Each Person",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4_content": "For services that let you choose workers, you'll see a list of people. Tap on each person to assign their worker:",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4_bullet1": "**Person 1:** Choose John (fade specialist)",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4_bullet2": "**Person 2:** Choose Sarah (braiding expert)",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4_bullet3": "**Person 3:** Choose Michael (kids cuts)",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4_bullet4": "**Person 4:** Choose John (same worker for multiple people)",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4Example_title": "Example: Different Workers for Different People",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step4Example_content": "**Family of 3 booking haircuts:**\n• Person 1 (Dad): Choose John (fade specialist)\n• Person 2 (Son): Choose Michael (great with kids)\n• Person 3 (Daughter): Choose Sarah (braiding expert)\n\nAll three will be served during your appointment block.",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5_title": "Step 5: Pick Your Time",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5_content": "When you select a date and time, the system will show slots that can accommodate ALL people in your group:",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5_bullet1": "**Regular View:** Shows slots for each service separately",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5_bullet2": "**Combined View:** Shows only slots where everyone can be served together",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5_bullet3": "**Duration:** The time shown includes all services for all people",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5Example_title": "Example: Time Calculation",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step5Example_content": "**Family booking:**\n• Haircut (45 min) × 2 people = 90 min\n• Braids (2 hours) × 1 person = 120 min\n• Buffer time between services = 15 min\n• **Total appointment time: 3 hours 45 min**\n\nThe system handles all this automatically!",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6_title": "Step 6: Payment",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6_content": "For group bookings, you pay:",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6_bullet1": "**30% deposit:** Calculated on the TOTAL cost of all services",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6_bullet2": "**Platform fee:** Small fixed fee (e.g., GHS 2) - charged ONCE for entire group",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6_bullet3": "**Remaining 70%:** Paid after all services are complete",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6_bullet4": "**Payment options:** Cash, card, mobile money, or app payment",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6Example_title": "Payment Example",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_step6Example_content": "**Family booking total: GHS 400**\n• Deposit at booking: GHS 120 (30% of GHS 400)\n• Platform fee: GHS 2 (charged once for entire group)\n• **Total to pay now: GHS 122**\n• Remaining after service: GHS 280\n• **Payment after:** Cash to worker/shop OR via app (your choice)",
  "docsGroupBookingsHowTo_important_content": "The deposit and platform fee are calculated on the TOTAL group booking, not per person. You pay once for the whole group.",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_intro_title": "One Worker or Multiple Workers?",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_intro_content": "When booking for a group, you have flexibility in how workers are assigned:",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_intro_bullet1": "**Same worker for everyone:** If one worker can handle everyone (sequentially)",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_intro_bullet2": "**Different workers:** Each person can have their preferred worker",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_intro_bullet3": "**Mix and match:** Some people share a worker, others have different ones",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_same_title": "Same Worker for Everyone",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_same_content": "If you choose the same worker for everyone, they will serve each person one after another. The total time is the sum of all services plus buffers.",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_different_title": "Different Workers for Different People",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_different_content": "When you choose different workers, they can work in parallel. This might reduce the total time needed. Example:",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_different_bullet1": "**Worker A:** Serves Person 1 (haircut)",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_different_bullet2": "**Worker B:** Serves Person 2 (braids) at the same time",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_different_bullet3": "**Worker A:** Then serves Person 3 (beard trim)",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_different_bullet4": "**Result:** Everyone finishes faster!",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_interface_title": "How to Assign Workers",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_interface_content": "In the worker selection screen, you'll see each person listed separately:",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_example_title": "What You'll See",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_example_content": "**For a group of 3 booking haircuts:**\n• **Person 1:** [Choose Worker] → John\n• **Person 2:** [Choose Worker] → Michael\n• **Person 3:** [Choose Worker] → John (again)\n\nTap each person to select their worker from the available list.",
  "docsGroupBookingsWorker_tip_content": "If a worker is already chosen for one person, they remain available for others unless fully booked. The system shows real-time availability.",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_calculation_title": "How Duration is Calculated",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_calculation_content": "For group bookings, the total appointment time is calculated based on:",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_calculation_bullet1": "**Service duration × quantity** for each service type",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_calculation_bullet2": "**Buffer time** between services (for cleanup)",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_calculation_bullet3": "**Parallel work** if multiple workers are assigned",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_sequential_title": "Example: Sequential (Same Worker)",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_sequential_content": "**One worker doing 3 haircuts (45 min each):**\n• Haircut 1: 9:00 - 9:45\n• Buffer: 9:45 - 9:50 (5 min)\n• Haircut 2: 9:50 - 10:35\n• Buffer: 10:35 - 10:40\n• Haircut 3: 10:40 - 11:25\n• **Total: 2 hours 25 min**",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_parallel_title": "Example: Parallel (Different Workers)",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_parallel_content": "**Three workers each doing one haircut (45 min each):**\n• Worker A: Person 1 (9:00 - 9:45)\n• Worker B: Person 2 (9:00 - 9:45) at same time\n• Worker C: Person 3 (9:00 - 9:45) at same time\n• **Total: 45 min**",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_combined_title": "Combined View for Groups",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_combined_content": "When booking for a group, Combined View is especially useful. It shows only time slots where ALL people in your group can be accommodated together, with the correct total duration.",
  "docsGroupBookingsTime_tip_content": "If your group is large or has many services, consider booking earlier in the day to ensure enough time before the shop closes.",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_deposit_title": "Deposit Calculation",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_deposit_content": "For group bookings, the 30% deposit is calculated on the **total cost of all services for all people**.",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_deposit_bullet1": "**Total cost:** Sum of all services × quantities",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_deposit_bullet2": "**Deposit:** 30% of total cost",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_deposit_bullet3": "**Platform fee:** One fixed fee for the entire group booking",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_deposit_bullet4": "**Total due now:** Deposit + platform fee",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_example_title": "Payment Example",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_example_content": "**Family of 4 with total GHS 500:**\n• Deposit (30%): GHS 150\n• Platform fee: GHS 2\n• **Pay now: GHS 152**\n• Pay after: GHS 350 (cash or app)",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_cancellation_title": "Cancellation for Groups",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_cancellation_content": "If you cancel a group booking:",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_cancellation_bullet1": "**Full group cancellation:** Entire deposit and fee are non-refundable",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_cancellation_bullet2": "**Partial cancellation:** If some people can't make it, you may lose their portion of the deposit",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_cancellation_bullet3": "**Rescheduling:** You can reschedule the whole group (deposit transfers)",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_important_content": "The platform fee is charged once per group booking, not per person. You save on fees by booking as a group! For example: 4 separate bookings = GHS 8 in fees, but 1 group booking = GHS 2 fee. You save GHS 6!",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_flexibility_title": "Flexible Payment After Service",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_flexibility_content": "After your group service, paying the remaining 70% is flexible:",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_flexibility_bullet1": "**One person pays all:** Pay total in cash or via app",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_flexibility_bullet2": "**Split the payment:** Each person pays their share in cash",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_flexibility_bullet3": "**Mix methods:** Some people use cash, others use app",
  "docsGroupBookingsPayment_flexibility_bullet4": "**Individual app payments:** Each person can pay their portion through the app",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_family_title": "Scenario 1: Family Haircut Day",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_family_content": "**The Mensah family (4 people) needs haircuts:**\n• Dad: Fade haircut (45 min, GHS 40)\n• Mom: Trim (30 min, GHS 35)\n• Son (10): Kids haircut (30 min, GHS 25)\n• Daughter (8): Braids (2 hours, GHS 80)\n\n**What they do:**\n1. Select \"Haircut\" → set quantity 3\n2. Select \"Braids\" → set quantity 1\n3. Choose workers: Dad → John, Son → Michael, Daughter → Sarah\n4. Pick a time that works for everyone\n5. Pay deposit: GHS 54 (30% of GHS 180) + GHS 2 fee = GHS 56\n6. After service, pay remaining GHS 126",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_friends_title": "Scenario 2: Friends Day Out",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_friends_content": "**Three friends want different services:**\n• Friend 1: Beard trim (30 min, GHS 25)\n• Friend 2: Haircut + Beard (75 min, GHS 65)\n• Friend 3: Full color (2 hours, GHS 120)\n\n**What they do:**\n1. Select each service with quantity 1\n2. Choose their preferred workers\n3. System finds a time that works for all\n4. Pay deposit: GHS 63 (30% of GHS 210) + GHS 2 fee = GHS 65",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_bridal_title": "Scenario 3: Bridal Party",
  "docsGroupBookingsScenarios_bridal_content": "**Bride + 3 bridesmaids getting ready:**\n• Bride: Hair + Makeup (3 hours, GHS 300)\n• Each bridesmaid: Hair styling (1 hour, GHS 80 each)\n\n**What they do:**\n1. Select Bride services with quantity 1\n2. Select Hair styling with quantity 3\n3. Assign different workers to each person\n4. Book a morning slot to have enough time\n5. Pay deposit: GHS 162 (30% of GHS 540) + GHS 2 fee = GHS 164",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq1Q": "What is a group booking?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq1A": "A group booking allows you to book services for multiple people at once. Instead of making separate bookings for each person, you can book everything together in one go. This is perfect for families, friends, or any group wanting services together.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq2Q": "How do I increase the number of people?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq2A": "After selecting a service, look for the **+** and **-** buttons. Tap **+** to increase the quantity (number of people) for that service. The price updates automatically. You cannot exceed the maximum quantity shown for that service.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq3Q": "Can we book different services for different people?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq3A": "Absolutely! You can select multiple services and set different quantities for each. For example, you can book 2 haircuts and 1 braid service all in the same booking. The system handles everything together.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq4Q": "Can different people have different workers?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq4A": "Yes! When you book for a group, you'll see each person listed separately. You can tap on each person to choose their preferred worker. This is great when different people have different preferences.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq5Q": "How is payment calculated for groups?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq5A": "The 30% deposit is calculated on the TOTAL cost of all services for all people. The platform fee is charged once for the entire group booking (not per person). After service, you pay the remaining 70% total (cash or app).",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq6Q": "What if one person cancels?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq6A": "If someone in your group cancels, the deposit for their portion is non-refundable. The rest of the group can still proceed. Contact the shop through the app to adjust the booking.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq7Q": "How is the total appointment time calculated?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq7A": "The system calculates total time based on: service durations × quantities, plus buffer times between services. If you choose different workers who can work in parallel, the total time may be shorter.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq8Q": "Is there a maximum group size?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq8A": "Each service has a maximum quantity limit shown when booking. If you need to book for a very large group, you may need to make multiple bookings or contact the shop directly.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq9Q": "Can I book for my children?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq9A": "Yes! Group bookings are perfect for families. You can book for yourself and your children together. Just set the quantity to include everyone. For kids services, look for \"Kids\" options.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq10Q": "How does check-in work for groups?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq10A": "When you arrive, let the shop know you have a group booking. They'll check the main booking and direct everyone to their assigned workers. Arrive 10-15 minutes early for large groups.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq11Q": "Can we split the payment?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq11A": "The deposit is paid by the person making the booking. After service, you can split the remaining 70% however you like - cash, individual app payments, or one person paying for all.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq12Q": "Can we reschedule a group booking?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq12A": "Yes, you can reschedule the entire group booking up to 24 hours before the appointment. The deposit transfers to the new time. If only some people need to reschedule, contact the shop.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq13Q": "Can we book as a group without an account?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq13A": "Yes! If the shop shares a group booking link, everyone can use it without downloading the app or creating accounts. The booking confirmation and receipt details are sent to your WhatsApp.",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq14Q": "Do we all have to pay in cash or can we use the app?",
  "docsGroupBookingsFaq14A": "You have full flexibility! You can pay the remaining 70% in cash (to the shop/worker), via the app individually, or any combination. Some people can pay cash while others use the app for their portion.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentOverview_title": "How Payment Works",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentOverview_subtitle": "Simple, transparent, secure",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentSummary_title": "Payment at a Glance",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentSummary_content": "Our payment system is designed to be fair for both clients and shop owners. Here's the simple breakdown:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentSummary_bullet1": "**30% Deposit:** Paid at booking to secure your appointment",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentSummary_bullet2": "**Platform Fee:** Small fixed fee (e.g., GHS 2) charged by the app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentSummary_bullet3": "**Remaining 70%:** Paid after your service is complete",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentSummary_bullet4": "**Two Ways to Pay Remaining:** Cash or via app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentExampleQuick_title": "Quick Example",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentExampleQuick_content": "**Service cost: GHS 100**\n• At booking: Pay GHS 30 (deposit) + GHS 2 (fee) = GHS 32\n• After service: Pay GHS 70 (cash or app)\n• Total to shop: GHS 100\n• Platform fee: GHS 2",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentImportant_content": "The platform fee is charged by the app, not the shop. It helps us maintain the platform and provide you with a great booking experience.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBookingNote_title": "Guest Booking (No App Download)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBookingNote_content": "Don't have the app? No problem! You can still book through your provider's booking link without creating an account. You pay the same 30% deposit + platform fee, and your receipt is sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositExplained_title": "The 30% Deposit",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositExplained_subtitle": "Why it's needed and how it works",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositWhy_title": "Why Do We Require a Deposit?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositWhy_content": "The 30% deposit protects both you and the shop:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositWhy_bullet1": "**For you:** Your slot is guaranteed – no one else can book it",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositWhy_bullet2": "**For the shop:** Workers are compensated if you cancel last minute",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositWhy_bullet3": "**For everyone:** Reduces no-shows, keeping prices fair",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositCalculation_title": "How the Deposit is Calculated",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositCalculation_content": "The deposit is always **30% of the total service cost**. This includes:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositCalculation_bullet1": "**Single service:** 30% of that service price",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositCalculation_bullet2": "**Multiple services:** 30% of all services combined",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositCalculation_bullet3": "**Group bookings:** 30% of total for all people",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositExamples_title": "Deposit Examples",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositExamples_content": "**Single Service:**\n• Haircut (GHS 45) → Deposit GHS 13.50\n\n**Multiple Services:**\n• Haircut (GHS 45) + Beard Trim (GHS 25) = GHS 70 total\n• Deposit: GHS 21\n\n**Group Booking (3 people):**\n• 3 × Haircut (GHS 45 each) = GHS 135 total\n• Deposit: GHS 40.50",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositNonRefundable_title": "Deposit Refund Policy",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositNonRefundable_content": "The 30% deposit is **non-refundable**. This means:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositNonRefundable_bullet1": "**If you cancel:** Deposit is not returned",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositNonRefundable_bullet2": "**If you don't show up:** Deposit is not returned",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositNonRefundable_bullet3": "**If you reschedule:** Deposit transfers to new time",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositNonRefundable_bullet4": "**If shop cancels:** Full deposit refunded",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedDepositWarning_content": "Please be sure about your booking before paying the deposit. While you can reschedule, the deposit cannot be refunded if you cancel.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPlatformFee_title": "Platform Fee",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPlatformFee_subtitle": "The small fee that keeps the app running",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeWhat_title": "What is the Platform Fee?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeWhat_content": "The platform fee is a small fixed charge (e.g., GHS 2) that goes to the app, not the shop. It covers:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeWhat_bullet1": "**App development** and maintenance",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeWhat_bullet2": "**Customer support** and dispute resolution",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeWhat_bullet3": "**Payment processing** costs",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeWhat_bullet4": "**New features** and improvements",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeHow_title": "How the Fee is Charged",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeHow_content": "Important things to know about the platform fee:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeHow_bullet1": "**Fixed amount** (not a percentage) – e.g., GHS 2 per booking",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeHow_bullet2": "**Charged once per booking** – not per service or per person",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeHow_bullet3": "**Non-refundable** – even if you cancel",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeHow_bullet4": "**Clearly shown** before you confirm payment",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeExamples_title": "Platform Fee Examples",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeExamples_content": "**Single person, one service:** GHS 2 fee\n**Single person, multiple services:** GHS 2 fee (still one booking!)\n**Family of 4 booking together:** GHS 2 fee (entire group)\n\n**Compare to booking separately:**\n• 4 separate bookings = 4 × GHS 2 = GHS 8 in fees\n• 1 group booking = GHS 2 fee – **you save GHS 6!**",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFeeTip_content": "Booking as a group saves you money on fees! Instead of paying the platform fee for each person, you pay just one fee for the entire group booking.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingPayment_title": "Paying the Remaining 70%",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingPayment_subtitle": "Two convenient options",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingOverview_title": "After Your Service",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingOverview_content": "Once your service is complete, you have two ways to pay the remaining 70%:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingOverview_bullet1": "**Option 1: Cash** – Pay the worker or shop directly",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingOverview_bullet2": "**Option 2: Via App** – Pay through the app using your preferred method",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingCash_title": "Paying with Cash",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingCash_content": "If you choose to pay the remaining balance in cash:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingCash_bullet1": "Simply hand the cash to your worker or at the counter",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingCash_bullet2": "You'll still receive a receipt through the app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingCash_bullet3": "The shop will mark the payment as received",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingCash_bullet4": "No additional fees",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_title": "Paying Through the App",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_content": "If you prefer to pay via the app:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_bullet1": "Open your booking in \"My Bookings\"",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_bullet2": "Tap \"Pay Remaining Balance\"",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_bullet3": "Choose your payment method (card, mobile money, etc.)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_bullet4": "Complete payment – instant confirmation",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingApp_bullet5": "Receipt saved in the app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingChoice_title": "Which Option Should You Choose?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingChoice_content": "**Choose cash if:** You prefer physical payment, have cash on hand, or want to tip in cash\n\n**Choose app if:** You want a digital record, don't carry cash, or prefer using mobile money/cards",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedRemainingImportant_content": "The remaining 70% is paid to the shop, not the platform. No additional platform fee is charged at this stage.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentTiming_title": "When Payments Happen",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentTiming_subtitle": "A timeline of when you pay",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineAtBooking_title": "At Booking Time",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineAtBooking_content": "**What you pay:**\n• 30% deposit\n• Platform fee (e.g., GHS 2)\n\n**What happens:** Your slot is secured immediately",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineBefore_title": "Before Appointment",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineBefore_content": "**Nothing to pay** – just show up at your scheduled time!\n\nYou'll receive reminders 24 hours and 1 hour before.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineAfter_title": "After Service",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineAfter_content": "**What you pay:**\n• Remaining 70% of total cost\n\n**How to pay:**\n• Cash (to worker or shop)\n• Via app (digital payment)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineSummary_title": "Payment Summary Example",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedTimelineSummary_content": "**Total bill: GHS 200**\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n**At booking:** GHS 60 (deposit) + GHS 2 (fee) = GHS 62\n**After service:** GHS 140 (remaining)\n**Total to shop:** GHS 200\n**Platform fee:** GHS 2",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancellationRefunds_title": "Cancellation & Refunds",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancellationRefunds_subtitle": "What happens when plans change",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelClient_title": "If You Cancel",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelClient_content": "**You cancel more than 24 hours before:**\n• Deposit: ❌ Non-refundable\n• Platform fee: ❌ Non-refundable\n• Remaining 70%: Not charged\n\n**You cancel within 24 hours:**\n• Deposit: ❌ Non-refundable\n• Platform fee: ❌ Non-refundable\n• Remaining 70%: Not charged\n• Note: Last-minute cancellations may affect your account standing",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelNoShow_title": "If You Don't Show Up",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelNoShow_content": "**No-show policy:**\n• Deposit: ❌ Forfeited\n• Platform fee: ❌ Forfeited\n• Remaining 70%: Not charged\n• Account: Marked as no-show\n• Repeated no-shows may result in account restrictions",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelShop_title": "If the Shop Cancels",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelShop_content": "**Shop cancels for any reason:**\n• Deposit: ✅ Full refund\n• Platform fee: ✅ Full refund\n• Remaining 70%: Not applicable\n• You'll receive notification and refund automatically",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelReschedule_title": "Rescheduling vs Cancelling",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelReschedule_content": "**Rescheduling** (changing time/date):\n• Deposit transfers to new booking\n• Platform fee transfers (no additional fee)\n• Available up to 24 hours before\n\n**Cancelling** (completely):\n• Deposit and fee are forfeited\n• Must rebook and pay deposit again",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedCancelTip_content": "If you can't make it, try to reschedule instead of cancelling. Your deposit transfers and you won't lose your money!",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupPayment_title": "Payment for Group Bookings",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupPayment_subtitle": "How it works when booking for multiple people",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupDeposit_title": "Deposit for Groups",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupDeposit_content": "For group bookings, the 30% deposit is calculated on the **total cost for everyone**.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupDeposit_bullet1": "**Example:** 4 people × GHS 50 each = GHS 200 total",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupDeposit_bullet2": "**Deposit:** 30% of GHS 200 = GHS 60",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupDeposit_bullet3": "**Paid by:** One person (the booker)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupFee_title": "Platform Fee for Groups",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupFee_content": "**Great news!** The platform fee is charged **once per booking**, not per person.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupFee_bullet1": "**Example:** Family of 4 booking together",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupFee_bullet2": "**Fee:** GHS 2 total (not GHS 8)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupFee_bullet3": "**Savings:** GHS 6 compared to booking separately",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupRemaining_title": "Paying the Remaining 70% for Groups",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupRemaining_content": "After the service, you have flexibility:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupRemaining_bullet1": "**One person pays all:** Pay total remaining in cash or app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupRemaining_bullet2": "**Split the bill:** Each person pays their share (cash to shop or individual app payments)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupRemaining_bullet3": "**Mix and match:** Some pay cash, others use app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupCancellation_title": "Group Cancellations",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupCancellation_content": "**If one person cancels:**\n• Their portion of the deposit is forfeited\n• The rest of the group can proceed\n• Contact shop to adjust\n\n**If entire group cancels:**\n• Full deposit and fee forfeited (standard policy)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupSaving_title": "Group Savings Example",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGroupSaving_content": "**Family of 4 booking separately vs together:**\n\n**Separate bookings:**\n• 4 × GHS 2 platform fee = GHS 8 in fees\n\n**Group booking:**\n• 1 × GHS 2 platform fee = GHS 2\n• **You save GHS 6!**",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentMethods_title": "Accepted Payment Methods",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentMethods_subtitle": "How you can pay",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsDeposit_title": "For Deposits (at booking)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsDeposit_content": "You can pay your deposit using:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsDeposit_bullet1": "**Credit/Debit Cards** (Visa, Mastercard, etc.)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsDeposit_bullet2": "**Mobile Money** (MTN, Vodafone, AirtelTigo)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsDeposit_bullet3": "**Bank Transfers** (instant payment)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsDeposit_bullet4": "**Apple Pay / Google Pay** (where available)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsRemaining_title": "For Remaining Balance (after service)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsRemaining_content": "After your service, you can pay the remaining 70% via:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsRemaining_bullet1": "**Cash** (pay directly to worker or shop)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsRemaining_bullet2": "**Mobile Money** (send to shop number)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsRemaining_bullet3": "**Card** (if shop has card reader)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsRemaining_bullet4": "**App Payment** (through the app)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsSecurity_title": "Payment Security",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsSecurity_content": "All payments through the app are:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsSecurity_bullet1": "**Encrypted** – your information is safe",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsSecurity_bullet2": "**PCI compliant** – meets security standards",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsSecurity_bullet3": "**Protected** – fraud monitoring in place",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsSecurity_bullet4": "**Receipt provided** – digital record of every payment",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedMethodsTip_content": "Save your payment details in the app for faster checkout next time!",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBookings_title": "Guest Bookings (No App Download)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBookings_subtitle": "Book without creating an account",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestWhat_title": "What is a Guest Booking?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestWhat_content": "A guest booking lets you reserve an appointment without downloading the app or creating an account. Your provider shares a link – you click it and book directly.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestPayment_title": "How Guest Booking Payment Works",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestPayment_content": "Guest bookings follow the same payment model as app bookings:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestPayment_bullet1": "**30% Deposit** – Pay upfront to secure your slot",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestPayment_bullet2": "**Platform Fee** – Small fixed fee added to deposit",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestPayment_bullet3": "**70% Balance** – Pay cash or online after service",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestWhatsapp_title": "Booking Details via WhatsApp",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestWhatsapp_content": "Once you complete your guest booking, your appointment details and payment receipt are sent to your WhatsApp. This way you can track everything without the app.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBenefits_title": "Why Book as a Guest?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBenefits_content": "Guest bookings are perfect if:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBenefits_bullet1": "You don't want to download another app",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBenefits_bullet2": "You're booking for a one-time appointment",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBenefits_bullet3": "You prefer simple, hassle-free booking",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestBenefits_bullet4": "Your provider shared a direct link with you",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestConvert_title": "Convert Guest to Account",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedGuestConvert_content": "If you make multiple bookings, you can create a full account anytime to access your booking history, saved payments, and loyalty benefits.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceipts_title": "Receipts & Records",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceipts_subtitle": "Keeping track of your payments",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_title": "What You'll Receive",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_content": "For every payment, you'll get:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_bullet1": "**Booking confirmation receipt** (at booking)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_bullet2": "**Deposit payment receipt** (immediate)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_bullet3": "**Final payment receipt** (after service)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_bullet4": "**Email copy** sent to your registered email",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptWhat_bullet5": "**In-app record** in \"My Bookings\"",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_title": "What's on Your Receipt",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_content": "Each receipt shows:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet1": "**Shop name** and location",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet2": "**Services booked** with quantities",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet3": "**Workers assigned**",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet4": "**Date and time** of appointment",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet5": "**Amount paid** (deposit/fee/remaining)",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet6": "**Payment method** used",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptInfo_bullet7": "**Transaction reference** number",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_title": "How to Access Receipts",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_content": "To view your payment history:",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_bullet1": "Go to **Profile** tab",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_bullet2": "Tap **Payment History**",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_bullet3": "See all transactions",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_bullet4": "Tap any receipt to view details",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedReceiptAccess_bullet5": "Share or download as PDF",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ_title": "Common Payment Questions",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ_subtitle": "Quick answers",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ1_title": "Is the deposit really non-refundable?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ1_content": "Yes, the 30% deposit is non-refundable by policy. This protects workers' time and discourages last-minute cancellations. The only exception is if the shop cancels on you.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ2_title": "Why a deposit instead of full payment?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ2_content": "The deposit system is designed to be fair to everyone:\n• **You:** Only pay 30% upfront, not the full amount\n• **Shop:** Gets some compensation if you cancel\n• **Workers:** Time is valued and protected",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ3_title": "Can I pay the full amount upfront?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ3_content": "Currently, we only collect the 30% deposit at booking. The remaining 70% is paid after service to ensure you're happy with the result before paying in full.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ4_title": "What if I want to add a tip?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedPaymentFAQ4_content": "Great question! Tips can be added when paying the remaining 70% via the app, or you can tip in cash directly to your worker. 100% of tips go to the worker.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq1Q": "Why is the deposit non-refundable?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq1A": "The deposit compensates workers for holding time exclusively for you. When you book a slot, that time can't be sold to someone else. The deposit policy discourages last-minute cancellations and no-shows, which helps keep prices fair for everyone.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq2Q": "What exactly is the platform fee for?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq2A": "The platform fee (e.g., GHS 2) helps us maintain the app, provide customer support, process payments securely, and develop new features. It's a small fixed fee that keeps the platform running smoothly for both clients and shops.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq3Q": "Can I really pay the remaining amount in cash?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq3A": "Yes! Many shops accept cash for the remaining 70%. You can also choose to pay through the app if you prefer digital payments. The choice is yours at the time of service.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq4Q": "How is the platform fee calculated for groups?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq4A": "The platform fee is charged **once per booking**, not per person. So if you book for a family of 4, you pay just one GHS 2 fee instead of four separate fees. This makes group bookings more economical!",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq5Q": "When would I get a refund?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq5A": "Refunds are issued only if the shop cancels your booking. In that case, both your deposit and platform fee are fully refunded. If you cancel, the deposit and fee are non-refundable by policy.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq6Q": "What payment methods are accepted?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq6A": "For deposits: Credit/debit cards, mobile money, bank transfers, and digital wallets. For remaining balance: Cash or any of the digital methods through the app. Available options may vary by region.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq7Q": "How do I tip my worker?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq7A": "You can tip your worker in two ways:\n1. **Cash:** Give directly to your worker after service\n2. **Via App:** Add a tip when paying the remaining 70%\n\n100% of tips go directly to your worker!",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq8Q": "How do I get a receipt?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq8A": "Receipts are automatically generated and sent to your email. You can also access all receipts in the app under Profile → Payment History. Each receipt shows full details of your transaction.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq9Q": "Can we split the bill for group bookings?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq9A": "Yes! For group bookings, you can split the remaining 70% however you like:\n• One person pays all (cash or app)\n• Each person pays their share (cash to shop)\n• Mix of cash and app payments\n\nThe deposit is paid by the person making the booking.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq10Q": "What if I have an emergency and can't make it?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq10A": "We understand emergencies happen. While the deposit is officially non-refundable, you can contact the shop directly through the app. Some shops may offer credit toward a future booking at their discretion. The platform fee cannot be refunded.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq11Q": "Can I save my payment details for faster booking?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq11A": "Yes! In your Profile settings, you can save payment methods securely. This makes future bookings faster – just confirm and pay with one tap. Your information is encrypted and stored securely.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq12Q": "Is my payment information secure?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq12A": "Absolutely. All payments are processed through secure, PCI-compliant gateways. Your payment details are encrypted and never stored in plain text. We use industry-standard security measures to protect your information.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq13Q": "What is a guest booking and do I need an account?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq13A": "A guest booking lets you reserve through a provider's shared link without downloading the app or creating an account. You pay the same 30% deposit + platform fee, and your receipt is sent to WhatsApp.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq14Q": "How do I get my booking details if I book as a guest?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq14A": "Your appointment details, payment receipt, and reminders are sent to your WhatsApp. You can access everything there without downloading the app.",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq15Q": "Can I convert my guest booking to a full account?",
  "docsPaymentFeesExplainedFaq15A": "Yes! After booking as a guest, you can create a full account anytime to access your booking history, saved payments, and other features like loyalty rewards."
}